latestIgtvVideos.title: 💻Long lasting everyday Work From Home Look #myrebootstory
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
•🔊The ongoing pandemic took a real toll on my health a few weeks back with long hectic hours at work, no recreation, stress of loved ones falling sick! 
🤒I myself fell very ill and it has taken a major toll on my skin with rashes , acne and redness settling in big time! 
🤞🏻But as I recover now I have taken charge of my mental and physical well-being!
😎I have decided to deck up as I used to for my regular work day and put in my best foot forward! 
@makeupforever Skin Equilizer primer and Reboot Foundation helped me achieve just that with it’s amazing Long lasting formula  Helps me look my best as I take on long long hours of work! 
This is a long lasting very simple basic work from home look ! #monochrome finish with Brown Eyes and Lips and simple pale @makeupforever Blush On.
Do try and let me know how it turns out! 🌸🌸💜💜

latestIgtvVideos.title: #letsgetindiaticking @titancompanyltd @titanwatchesindia
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🇮🇳India is known for its people & by its people! When we all decide to come together in whichever way possible, only then can our country rise to its full potential!🤝🤝
The last few months have turned us all into a mode where we keep spending ONLY on the basics! Without realising that the non basic commodities we are shying away from helps running the families of thousands of those who depend on their sales! Let’s look at a wider picture and realise we can never grow unless we grow as a community!🇮🇳🇮🇳

Let’s get together and support such #localbusinesses 

#letsgetindiaticking , as every single purchase you make, has the power to ignite hope and foster the dreams of millions of people. 👫🏻👭🏻👬🏿👭🏻👫🏻🧍🏻‍♂️🧍🏻‍♀️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Fellow Humans of India 🇮🇳
Holi Hain Sabki @goldmedalindia
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Did you know according to a global report released by Non-Profit Organisation WaterAid, 600 million Indians live in areas where water scarcity ranges from high to extreme?
This Holi, let us think about Indians battling drought and water scarcity, while we celebrate the festival of colours that brings out the Country’s 'vibrancy'. Let’s pledge to play this Holi responsibly and make it happy for everyone.

As I take the @goldmedalindia Pledge - #HoliIsForAll. I nominate @aneekroychowdhury @mitraniket @dentist_story to carry forward the pledge by sharing this video.
